{
  "info": {
    "name": "HT-CentralCashPool-CLM-Mirror-TimeEpoch-BiWeekly-12",
    "_postman_id": "ht-v16-4m-correct-alloc-breach-sell",
    "description": "HT v16 — $4M Pool · useFixedQuantity=true · Bands 20%/25%/30% unchanged · Correct SELL at May-15\n\n  WHAT CHANGED FROM v14/v15 (and why):\n  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\n  1. useFixedQuantity: TRUE  (was false in v14)\n     false → ADM uses contractNP / portfolioNAV  (capital-ratio, price-blind)\n     true  → ADM uses positionQuantity × spotPrice / portfolioNAV  (market-value ratio)\n\n     WHY THIS MATTERS:\n     With false and NP=$1M: as BTC rises from $50K→$78K, NP stays $1M,\n     so alloc = 1M / NAV ≈ 12–20% forever. Price moves are invisible.\n     With true and qty=20: as BTC rises, 20×price grows → alloc correctly\n     rises from 25% toward 30%, triggering SELL when price crosses $75K.\n\n  2. Pool reduced $8M → $4M  (bands and T-Bills unchanged)\n     WHY: With useFixedQuantity=true and bands min=20%/target=25%/max=30%,\n     for each ADM to start AT TARGET after deployment:\n       positionQty × entryPrice / portfolioNAV = targetAllocation\n       20 × $50,000 / NAV = 0.25  →  NAV must equal $4,000,000\n\n     At entry, NAV = 40 BTC × $50K + nonBTC_base = $4M\n     So nonBTC_base must = $2,000,000.\n\n     nonBTC_base = cash_residual + T-Bills_at_purchase\n     T-Bills (same as before) = $988,113\n     cash_residual = $2,000,000 - $988,113 = $1,011,887\n     Pool = $2M (CLMs) + $988,113 (T-Bills) + $1,011,887 (cash) = $4,000,000\n\n     With the original $8M pool, nonBTC would be $6M,\n     NAV = $8M, each ADM would see 20×50K/8M = 12.5% (at MIN floor),\n     and BUY signals would fire again. $4M is the exact right size.\n\n  3. BTC price path steepened\n     Breach triggers when: 20×P / (40×P + 2,000,000) > 0.30\n     Solving: P > $75,000\n     Price path reaches $78,000 at May-15 → clean breach at that epoch.\n     Post-sell price eases to $74K (May-31) → stays in band through Aug.\n\n  ALLOCATION STORY (per ADM, useFixedQuantity=true, qty=20 BTC):\n  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n  Feb-28 (CASH-PAM IED)    0 BTC deployed       alloc = 0.0%  (pool cash only)\n  Mar-01 (CLM-Lend IED)   +20 BTC @ $50K        alloc = 25.0% (20×50K / 4M = target)\n  Mar-01 (CLM-Spot IED)   +20 BTC @ $50K        alloc = 25.0% (20×50K / 4M = target, same)\n  Mar-15 ($55K)            40 BTC steady         alloc = 26.2% (20×55K / 4.2M)\n  Mar-31 ($60K)            40 BTC steady         alloc = 27.3% (20×60K / 4.4M)\n  Apr-15 ($65K)            40 BTC steady         alloc = 28.3% (20×65K / 4.6M)\n  Apr-30 ($70K)            40 BTC steady         alloc = 29.2% (20×70K / 4.8M)  near ceiling\n  May-15 ($78K)  BREACH    40 BTC pre-sell       alloc = 30.5% (20×78K / 5.12M) > 30% MAX\n    → ad_btc01_spot SELL fires: sell 3.59 BTC per CLM @ $78K = $280K returned\n    → ad_btc01 (lending) also fires: sell 3.59 BTC @ $78K = $280K returned\n    → post-sell per CLM: 16.41 BTC × $78K / $5.12M = 25.0% (back at target)\n    → combined: 32.82 BTC total\n  May-31 ($74K)            32.82 BTC post-sell   alloc = 26.8% (16.41×74K / 4.43M) in band\n  Jun-01              TBILL-3mo-400K matures → +$400K to CASH-PAM\n  Jun-30 ($90K)            32.82 BTC             alloc = 29.8% (16.41×90K / 4.95M) near ceiling but no breach\n  Jul-01              TBILL-4mo-350K matures → +$350K to CASH-PAM\n  Aug-01              TBILL-5mo-250K matures → +$250K to CASH-PAM\n  Aug-31 ($65K)            32.82 BTC             alloc = 25.8% (16.41×65K / 4.13M) near target, all settle\n\n  SCENARIO: ht_v16_4m_fixedqty_scn01   STEPS: 11   CONTRACTS: 6",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
